      "clinical_note": "Pre-operative evaluation for TKA. Labs reviewed: CBC normal, BMP normal, HgA1c 7.1 (acceptable for surgery). EKG: NSR. Chest X-ray: clear. Discussed surgical risks including infection, DVT, and hardware failure. Patient understands and consents. Surgical date scheduled 02/15/2024."
