      "clinical_note": "Right L4-L5 transforaminal epidural steroid injection performed under fluoroscopic guidance. AP and lateral views confirmed needle placement at right L4-5 foramen. Contrast injection showed epidural spread without vascular uptake. Injected: 80mg methylprednisolone + 1cc 0.25% bupivacaine. Patient tolerated well. Post-procedure: vital signs stable, no immediate complications. Discharge instructions provided."
    },
